@nazo you'll need to change the commit message from `[AIRFLOW-XXX]pymysql pendulum fix` to
`[AIRFLOW-4501] pymysql pendulum fix converters datetime bug`

The logs for releases are generated from the commit message so it's important it will be accurate.

